<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Appointment Confirmation</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            margin: 20px;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .container {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }
        h1 {
            color: #333333;
        }
        p {
            color: #555555;
        }
        .appointment-details {
            border-top: 2px solid #cccccc;
            margin-top: 20px;
            padding-top: 20px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Appointment Successfully Reserved</h1>
        <p>Dear [Patient Name],</p>
        <p>Your appointment has been successfully reserved with ABC Laboratories.</p>
        
        <div class="appointment-details">
            <p><strong>Appointment ID:</strong> [Your Appointment ID]</p>
            <p><strong>Appointment Date and Time:</strong> [Date and Time]</p>
            <p><strong>Branch:</strong> [Test Number]</p>
        </div>

        <p>For any inquiries or changes, please contact our customer service.</p>

        <p>Thank you for choosing ABC Laboratories. We look forward to serving you.</p>

        <p>Best Regards,<br>ABC Laboratories Team</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
